## Required Focus Group Response Schema

Respond ONLY with a YAML block matching this exact schema. No prose before or after.

```yaml
persona_name: "{{ persona_name }}"
uxw_id: "{{ uxw_id }}"
score: {{ score }}  # integer 1-10

what_i_loved:
  - "[specific positive moment, in persona voice]"
  - "[specific positive moment, in persona voice]"

what_made_me_quit:
  - "[specific friction or blocker, in persona voice]"
  - "[specific friction or blocker, in persona voice]"

top_3_must_fixes:
  - "[must-fix #1 — most critical, actionable]"
  - "[must-fix #2]"
  - "[must-fix #3]"

segment_specific_concern: |
  [What concerns this persona that other segments might not share. Be segment-specific.]

would_pay: "{{ would_pay }}"  # yes | no | conditional
would_pay_reason: |
  [Why they would or would not pay, in their voice. If conditional, state the condition.]
```
